{"lastModified":1764335811162,"uri":"c::8181076994::vessel::d5cc77bc-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Summer Operating Area: West Mediterranean - Naples/Sicily, Riviera/Corsica/Sardinia\nWinter Operating Area: British Virgin Islands, U.S. Virgin Islands, Leeward Islands, Windward Islands\n\nLISA OF THE SEAS is a 20.46m / 67ft Catamaran Luxury Yacht built in 2020 by Fountaine Pajot. Sleeping 10 guests in 5 cabins and with a crew of 3. The guest cabins comprise of 5 cabins with a queen size bed and en-suite bathroom facilities.","blueprint":{"name":"LISA OF THE SEAS","images":["/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::d5cc77bc-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::795f0b70-a994-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::d5cc77bc-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7a1bf2d0-a994-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::d5cc77bc-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7af514c0-a994-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::d5cc77bc-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7bed0950-a994-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::d5cc77bc-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7ccc1eb0-a994-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::d5cc77bc-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7dac4580-a994-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::d5cc77bc-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7e80ac80-a994-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::d5cc77bc-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::80420b90-a994-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8181076994::vessel::d5cc77bc-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::81306330-a994-11ee-9bb5-414bf146c92b.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::81810